{"tid":1326541,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連仔del咗我嘅勇武Po?","createTime":"2019-07-17T09:07:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T12:10:57.000Z","uid":177213,"like":393,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"56877198844605a22a6682df15b2dbeeb624b377","tid":1326541,"uid":177213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T09:07:32.000Z","msg":"是咁的，<br />\n<br />\n小弟早前打咗篇集思廣益嘅義士須知(都算有2千幾個正皮)，<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KGm4P99.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKGm4P99.png&h=69160ac6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過唔知點解啱啱打算入去睇返少少嘢嗰陣，開返寫Po紀錄竟然搵唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n入返之前save低嘅link又長load入唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［唔想死必睇］新手義士基本須知<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1243561\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1243561</a><br />\n<br />\n(入到嘅請留言通知)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個account係人哋同我共用嘅，<br />\n<br />\n照我所知連登除咗連仔之外自己係del唔到Po，<br />\n<br />\n想問有冇人知可以點解決？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ec69f5c452766000ab63c35103ce1cf427d8391","tid":1326541,"uid":177213,"like":28,"dislike":3,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T09:07:56.000Z","msg":"各位721金鐘見"},{"pid":"6e7d239a1c848e360aef5101b4242a8a94be2a0f","tid":1326541,"uid":177213,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T09:08:26.000Z","msg":"請問連仔喺唔喺度？"},{"pid":"5e3f04e58e2cd8df244c8612b856e5cfda8b5d00","tid":1326541,"uid":153258,"like":91,"dislike":2,"score":89,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T09:08:57.000Z","msg":"點解唔開係站務台"},{"pid":"9a988dc2610725a5405ca560cd11db72d55fbe9e","tid":1326541,"uid":4493,"like":294,"dislike":3,"score":291,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T09